  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 375 degrees Fahrenheit",
    "Roll out the phyllo dough and cut into 4 equal pieces",
    "In a bowl, mix together the diced nectarines, crumbly feta cheese, honey, olive oil, salt, black pepper, and rose water",
    "Place a spoonful of the nectarine mixture onto one corner of each phyllo piece",
    "Fold the phyllo into a triangle and press the edges to seal",
    "Place the tarts into 4 ramekins and brush the tops with olive oil",
    "Bake the tarts for 25 minutes or until golden brown",
    "Remove from the oven and let cool for 10 minutes before serving"
  ],
